      List<Lecture> loadData(String path, String configPath) throws IOException
      Loads schedule data from an external file.
      Parameters:
      path - The path from which to load the schedule data.
      configPath - The path to the configuration file, if applicable.
      Returns:
      List<Lecture> returns if the data loading is successful.
      Throws:
      IOException - If an I/O error occurs during the data loading process.
